    The purpose of this template is to render a row in the legend table for the weekend calculator.

    Required context variables:
    - lefttext | string | the text for the left cell
    - righttext | string | the text for the right cell
    Optional context variables:
    - leftclass | string | any class for the left cell
    - rightclass | string | any class for the right cell
}}

<tr>
    <td {{# leftclass }}class="{{ leftclass }}"{{/ leftclass }}>{{ lefttext }}</td>
    <td {{# rightclass }}class="{{ rightclass }}"{{/ rightclass }}>{{ righttext }}</td>
</tr>
